{"tid":674292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「點解參與者愈嚟愈少？」 民政處問區議員去六四晚會否","createTime":"2018-05-22T14:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T01:45:34.000Z","uid":51546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f7bc89c410c65fd03eaf3fbe1c25792f02bf9d06","tid":674292,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】今年係六四事件29周年，工黨屯門區議員譚駿賢喺facebook貼文，話噚日收到民政事務處職員電話，問佢會唔會舉辦六四相關活動、出席維園集會，更問佢點解參與六四集會嘅人愈嚟愈少。譚駿賢一頭霧水，質疑呢啲問題同地區事務有咩關係，問呢類政治取向嘅意見又有何作用，話「我唔知，亦諗唔到」。<br />\n譚駿賢：同地區事務何干？<br />\n譚駿賢透露，民政處職員每月都會致電佢，詢問區務意見，佢對有途徑反映居民聲音唔反感，但質疑職員點解要問六四相關問題。提倡「結束一黨專政」可唔可以參舉近期引起討論，譚駿賢噚日同時講明自己會繼續出席六四晚會、「繼續嗌結束中共一黨專政」，反問「夠清楚未？」<br />\n民主黨屯門區議員何杏梅向Emily透露，自己都收到民政處職員查詢，問佢估計有幾多人參加六四晚會，佢就答對方「我點知」。何杏梅話，職員過去都有向區議員問政府政策或《施政報告》內容等意見，評估民情，但佢首次收到有關六四嘅詢問，相信對方係按上級指示問議員，形容職員此舉「好奇怪」。對於有網民質疑，係咪有人想蒐證，作為撤銷佢哋參選資格（DQ）嘅「罪證」，何杏梅話無謂去估原因，因為如果真係要DQ佢哋，政府搵唔同藉口都得，例如參加過佔中。<br />\n民政處：會就熱議議題聽意見<br />\n民政處回覆Emily查詢，話佢哋其中一項主要工作係喺社區建立同維持網絡聯繫，「以了解市民的需要和期望」。該處又話喺正式或非正式場合與不同人士聯絡交流時，會就當時社會關注同熱議嘅議題，聆聽不同人嘅睇法及意見。"},{"pid":"0c7679d5ec6cd66d490d7c02240a49b3a14ebee6","tid":674292,"uid":20227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4d7ec5dbb5888e6a77ee1f07bbb4b36fbcd1838","tid":674292,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850169ab9cf48286c4eb66f7e1bbdb2cd144cc08","tid":674292,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"問嗰個真係on9<br />\nchok人冇技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3485191cfee2508ea9c6a4ef67829963c047746","tid":674292,"uid":56698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"850169ab9cf48286c4eb66f7e1bbdb2cd144cc08","tid":674292,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"問嗰個真係on9<br />\nchok人冇技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"求其問咗交差啫"},{"pid":"6e396cc32ac0f844d2adb44f9412eb834213777e","tid":674292,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:15:00.000Z","msg":"支那急了。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會？ 支那同胞聯會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeab462abaf1b94869aec5ef2ac1cdabfd6425b","tid":674292,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">間接認證六四維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"5d30d93a1f2e94c69053c342a8fc594d1d7e37ff","tid":674292,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"因為冇撚用囉屌你老母正一死傻鳩"},{"pid":"54cf6120c9e28f8dfd81c3cec8de927531553b8a","tid":674292,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"想問下每年六四集會有無申請不反對書？"},{"pid":"555a6d1d166f05624c47c8297011fe7028c6160d","tid":674292,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a01f1cf4be7681fb4f87b1e21cfa29043c5d6f","tid":674292,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b726e08da59b34102e88e5c76ddb080853b5b48","tid":674292,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img s